The evidence with the title 'A revolution: the Netherlands kisses gas goodbye ' says Jun 7, 2017  ... In climate policy debates , the focus is often on electricity generation, and  ... New houses will not be connected to the gas grid anymore in anycase . The 7 million existing houses will be gradually disconnected from the gas grid .  ... So how does the Netherlands intend to heat its homes in 2050 if not by gas ? 
